WEBVTT

00:10.534 --> 00:11.732
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:11.734 --> 00:13.198
HAVE I MADE THAT MUCH ALREADY?

00:13.200 --> 00:15.865
I SAID,
"WHO'S USING WHO, JAMES?"

00:15.867 --> 00:17.265
I'LL NEVER DOUBT YOU AGAIN.

00:17.267 --> 00:18.598
WE'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS,

00:18.600 --> 00:19.732
THOUGH, ABOUT A GIRL
WHO LIVED HERE ONCE.

00:19.734 --> 00:20.898
ROCHELLE CROSS.

00:20.900 --> 00:23.132
THE SISTERS,
ROCHELLE AND TARA,

00:23.134 --> 00:25.565
BUT CROSS WASN'T
THEIR LAST NAME.

00:25.567 --> 00:27.532
-WHAT WAS IT?
-JAMES.

00:27.534 --> 00:29.432
-ROCHELLE CROSS.
-WHAT ABOUT HER?

00:29.434 --> 00:31.499
DADDY, SHE IS
GERALD JAMES' DAUGHTER.

00:31.501 --> 00:33.898
SHE'S THE HALF-SISTER
OF BASIE SKANKS.

00:33.900 --> 00:35.032
BASIE.

00:35.034 --> 00:37.999
I HEARD YOU BEEN A BAD GIRL.

00:38.001 --> 00:40.431
IF I THOUGHT I COULD LOSE
THIS CASE, CORALIE,

00:40.433 --> 00:41.699
I WOULDN'T TAKE IT.

00:41.701 --> 00:44.032
OKAY, I'LL DO IT.

00:44.034 --> 00:46.232
WELL, YOU COULDN'T EVEN TELL
SOME HOE ON THE RADIO

00:46.234 --> 00:47.831
THAT WE WERE TOGETHER.

00:47.833 --> 00:50.632
I'LL CLAIM YOU WHEN YOU START
ACTING LIKE SOMEONE

00:50.634 --> 00:53.499
WHO DESERVES ME.

00:53.501 --> 00:55.299
-IT'S ABOUT THE ACCOUNTS.
-WHAT?

00:55.301 --> 00:57.365
OVER $200,000 WAS DEPOSITED

00:57.367 --> 01:00.365
INTO IT OVER THE PAST
THREE MONTHS, THEN WITHDRAWN,

01:00.367 --> 01:02.598
BUT I CAN'T SEEM
TO FIND WHERE IT WENT.

01:02.600 --> 01:03.931
WHAT DO YOU WANT, LIONEL?

01:03.933 --> 01:05.999
I WANT TO TALK
ABOUT MY DAUGHTER.

01:06.001 --> 01:11.332
♪♪

01:11.334 --> 01:12.798
COME ON, NOW.

01:12.800 --> 01:15.198
I'M NOT GONNA WASTE
THIS WHOLE WEEK

01:15.200 --> 01:19.932
PROPPING UP A FLOPPY OLD PUPPET
WITH ONE DANGLY EYE.

01:19.934 --> 01:22.665
MY REPUTATION IS ON THE LINE
HERE TOO, GIRL.

01:22.667 --> 01:25.665
YOU'VE GOT TO SELL THIS THING.

01:25.667 --> 01:26.798
SIT DOWN.

01:26.800 --> 01:34.765
♪♪

01:34.767 --> 01:36.632
WHEN JAMES CHEATED
WITH MAVIS --

01:36.634 --> 01:39.298
I STILL DON'T KNOW
WHY YOU STAYED AFTER THAT.

01:39.300 --> 01:42.165
I LEAVE A MAN IF HE SCRAPES
HIS FORK TOO LOUD ON HIS PLATE.

01:42.167 --> 01:45.432
I WANTED TO LEAVE HIM, AT LEAST
FOR A LITTLE WHILE, YOU KNOW,

01:45.434 --> 01:47.898
TO SCARE HIM,

01:47.900 --> 01:49.932
BUT THEN WE HAD
THIS ANNUAL VACATION

01:49.934 --> 01:53.465
COMING UP
WITH LIONEL AND PATRICE.

01:53.467 --> 01:55.065
THE LIONEL YOU HAD
YOUR FLING WITH?

01:55.067 --> 01:57.499
YES, AND THAT'S ALL IT
WAS MEANT TO BE, WAS A FLING.

01:57.501 --> 02:00.099
I MEAN, I JUST NEEDED TO GET
MY GROOVE BACK A LITTLE.

02:00.101 --> 02:01.565
MM-HMM.

02:01.567 --> 02:03.498
-BUT THEN I GOT PREGNANT.
-NO.

02:03.500 --> 02:06.632
AND NOW THAT LIONEL IS DYING,
HE WANTS TO TELL THE WOMAN

02:06.634 --> 02:10.098
THAT HE'S SURE IS
HIS DAUGHTER THE TRUTH.

02:10.100 --> 02:12.665
-GRACE?
-WHO ELSE?

02:12.667 --> 02:15.798
I'M TELLING YOU,
GOD HAS IT IN FOR ME.

02:15.800 --> 02:18.031
IS SHE REALLY HIS DAUGHTER?

02:18.033 --> 02:23.499
THE TIMING OF IT WOULD SEEM
TO INDICATE THAT...

02:25.267 --> 02:27.332
OH, MAXINE,
THIS SELFISH OLD MAN

02:27.334 --> 02:29.732
WANTS TO DIE LIKE
AN EXILED PATRIARCH,

02:29.734 --> 02:31.732
LEAVING ME BEHIND
WITH THIS GIRL BLAMING ME.

02:31.734 --> 02:33.265
FOR WHAT, NOT TELLING HER?

02:33.267 --> 02:34.865
OH, SHE'S GONNA THINK,

02:34.867 --> 02:37.798
"OH, THIS IS THE KEY
TO ALL MY SORROWS.

02:37.800 --> 02:41.132
"THIS IS MY ANSWER TO LIFE.
MY MOTHER, THE WHORE,

02:41.134 --> 02:42.532
WAS ASHAMED OF ME,"
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

02:42.534 --> 02:44.299
SHE WOULDN'T BE
COMPLETELY WRONG.

02:44.301 --> 02:46.532
LOOK, YOU KNOW WHAT
YOU GOT TO DO, MAE.

02:46.534 --> 02:47.998
DRINK BLEACH AND WALK
INTO TRAFFIC?

02:48.000 --> 02:49.665
YOU GOT TO GET AHEAD OF IT.

02:49.667 --> 02:52.698
YOU'RE ABOUT TO STEP
INTO THE HOLY OF HOLIES.

02:52.700 --> 02:55.498
PASTOR, YOU GOT
TO GET YOURSELF CLEAN.

02:55.500 --> 02:59.132
SECRETS HAVE NO PLACE
IN THE COMPANY OF THE KING.

03:02.333 --> 03:07.665
