03:07.667 --> 03:11.798
♪ AMEN ♪

03:11.800 --> 03:14.998
♪ OOH, OOH ♪

03:15.000 --> 03:24.065
♪♪

03:24.067 --> 03:30.732
♪♪

03:30.734 --> 03:34.065
