03:45.267 --> 03:48.865
♪♪

03:48.867 --> 03:50.465
WHEN ROCHELLE'S MOTHER
WENT TO PRISON,

03:50.467 --> 03:52.265
SHE AND HER SISTER WOUND
UP IN FOSTER CARE,

03:52.267 --> 03:54.598
SO I WENT TO SEE THEIR LAST
FOSTER MOTHER YESTERDAY.

03:54.600 --> 03:57.132
NOW, THIS FORM FROM CHILD
PROTECTIVE SERVICES

03:57.134 --> 04:00.132
SHOWS THAT THE FLANNERYS
TOOK IN TWO GIRLS

04:00.134 --> 04:03.198
26 YEARS AGO,
ROCHELLE AND TARA,

04:03.200 --> 04:05.199
AND THE FOSTER MOTHER CONFIRMS

04:05.201 --> 04:09.265
THAT THE GIRLS' LAST NAME
AT THE TIME WAS JAMES.

04:09.267 --> 04:10.765
A BEWITCHING COINCIDENCE.

04:10.767 --> 04:12.798
DADDY,
THE DETAILS ALL LINE UP.

04:12.800 --> 04:14.132
THEIR FATHER DIED IN A FIRE.

04:14.134 --> 04:16.131
MOTHER WENT TO PRISON.
IT ALL FITS PERFECTLY,

04:16.133 --> 04:17.831
AND THEN THE FOSTER MOM
GAVE ME THIS PICTURE.

04:17.833 --> 04:20.365
THAT IS ROCHELLE.

04:20.367 --> 04:22.498
IT JUST DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

04:22.500 --> 04:25.298
FACTS ARE FACTS.

04:25.300 --> 04:28.032
AND WHAT ABOUT BASIE SKANKS?

04:28.034 --> 04:29.432
HE WAS THEIR HALF-BROTHER.

04:29.434 --> 04:31.398
FOSTER MOM REMEMBERS
HEARING THEM TALK ABOUT HIM.

04:31.400 --> 04:33.465
HE WAS THEIR HERO.

04:33.467 --> 04:38.532
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

04:38.534 --> 04:41.465
IT JUST DOESN'T SEEM POSSIBLE.

04:41.467 --> 04:44.532
WHY IS THIS SO HARD
FOR YOU TO BELIEVE?

04:44.534 --> 04:47.198
BECAUSE...

04:47.200 --> 04:48.999
BECAUSE WHY?
IT'S ALL THERE, DADDY.

04:49.001 --> 04:51.399
BECAUSE OF EVERYTHING
THAT ROCHELLE HAS DONE,

04:51.401 --> 04:55.198
BECAUSE OF THE WAY SHE CARRIES
HERSELF IN MY COMPANY.

04:55.200 --> 04:57.399
SHE'S A VIRTUOUS WOMAN,
AND I JUST --

04:57.401 --> 05:01.798
I JUST CAN'T BELIEVE IT'S TRUE.

05:01.800 --> 05:03.832
SHE RAISED MONEY
FOR YOUR DEFENSE FUND.

05:03.834 --> 05:06.365
SHE DONATED GENEROUSLY
TO OUR CHURCH.

05:06.367 --> 05:08.898
SHE HELPED ME PAY OFF THE IRS.

05:08.900 --> 05:12.932
NOW, IF SHE IS THE VENGEFUL
PERSON THAT YOU SAY SHE IS,

05:12.934 --> 05:15.932
WHY WOULD SHE DO THAT?
WHY?

05:15.934 --> 05:17.998
WAIT A MINUTE, NOW.

05:18.000 --> 05:19.332
I'M SORRY.
THEY WON'T LISTEN.

05:19.334 --> 05:21.799
-WHO WON'T LISTEN?
-FBI.

05:21.801 --> 05:23.132
-FBI?
-YES, MA'AM.

05:23.134 --> 05:24.532
-PLEASE STEP ASIDE.
-YOU JUST STOP RIGHT THERE.

05:24.534 --> 05:25.698
WE HAVE A SEARCH
AND SEIZURE WARRANT, MA'AM.

05:25.700 --> 05:26.832
PLEASE STEP ASIDE.

05:26.834 --> 05:28.432
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT?

05:28.434 --> 05:30.099
YOU'RE BEING INVESTIGATED
ON SUSPICION OF BANK FRAUD,

05:30.101 --> 05:32.032
THEFT, AND EMBEZZLEMENT
OF CHURCH FUNDS.

05:32.034 --> 05:34.298
WE'RE HERE TO CONFISCATE
ANY COMPUTERS, DISKS, FILES,

05:34.300 --> 05:36.532
OR ANY PAPERWORK WE DEEM
RELEVANT TO THE INVESTIGATION.

05:36.534 --> 05:38.065
BUT WE WEREN'T THE ONES
WHO WERE --

05:38.067 --> 05:40.332
I'M GONNA ASK YOU
TO PLEASE STEP OUTSIDE NOW.

05:40.334 --> 05:41.465
JACOB.

05:41.467 --> 05:42.598
LET'S JUST LET THESE FOLKS
DO THEIR JOB.

05:42.600 --> 05:45.265
LET'S GO.

05:45.267 --> 05:48.532
COME ON.

05:48.534 --> 05:50.865
OH, ONE MORE THING,
MR. GREENLEAF.

05:50.867 --> 05:52.665
THAT'S PASTOR GREENLEAF.

05:52.667 --> 05:55.331
RIGHT. I ASSUME YOU
HAVE AN ACCOUNTANT.

05:55.333 --> 05:56.732
OF COURSE WE DO.

05:56.734 --> 05:58.132
I'M AGENT KRENSHAW, FBI.

05:58.134 --> 06:00.132
WE HAVE A FEW QUESTIONS
WE NEED TO ASK YOU.

06:00.134 --> 06:02.332
THANK GOODNESS YOU'RE HERE.

06:02.334 --> 06:05.665
THERE'S SOMETHING GOING ON HERE
THAT'S HIGHLY UNORTHODOX.

06:05.667 --> 06:07.465
LET ME SHOW YOU.

06:07.467 --> 06:14.932
♪♪

06:14.934 --> 06:16.265
A DAY WITH LADY MAE?

06:16.267 --> 06:17.732
NOW, THAT WAS
A WONDERFUL TRADITION,

06:17.734 --> 06:21.065
BUT THIS IS GOING TO BE
A COMPLETE UPGRADE.

06:21.067 --> 06:24.265
-WELL, TELL ME.
-SHE CHANGES EVERYTHING.

06:24.267 --> 06:27.132
-THAT'S THE NAME OF THE EVENT?
-YES.

06:27.134 --> 06:30.198
AND IT'S GOING TO BE A DAY
OF RENEWAL AND REDEDICATION,

06:30.200 --> 06:34.732
PREACHING AND TEACHING,
SINGING AND HOLY DANCING.

06:34.734 --> 06:36.065
-AMEN.
-YES. AMEN.

06:36.067 --> 06:38.532
WILL YOUR DAUGHTER
BE SPEAKING?

06:38.534 --> 06:39.932
CHARITY WILL BE SINGING, YES.

06:39.934 --> 06:41.698
NO, I MEAN PASTOR GREENLEAF,

06:41.700 --> 06:44.231
YOUR FAMOUS DIRECTOR
OF OUTREACH.

06:44.233 --> 06:46.299
A FEW MONTHS AGO,
SHE WAS HAILED IN THE PAPER

06:46.301 --> 06:47.899
AS THE NEW FACE OF CALVARY.

06:47.901 --> 06:49.698
SHE MIGHT MAKE AN APPEARANCE.

06:49.700 --> 06:51.998
SHE WON'T.

06:52.000 --> 06:54.932
I MEAN, THIS FABULOUS
ROSTER OF SPEAKERS

06:54.934 --> 06:56.765
WE HAVE IS FULL AS IT IS.

06:56.767 --> 06:59.999
BUT WITH THIS LEGAL FUND OF HERS
MAKING FRONT PAGE NEWS,

07:00.001 --> 07:02.998
FOLKS WILL BE WANTING TO HEAR
WHAT SHE'S UP TO NOW.

07:03.000 --> 07:04.465
WON'T SHE BE SPEAKING?

07:04.467 --> 07:09.065
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:09.067 --> 07:11.265
HERE'S WHAT I CAN TELL YOU.

07:11.267 --> 07:14.465
THE SPIRIT OF GOD
WILL BE UP THERE SPEAKING.

07:14.467 --> 07:18.065
NO MATTER WHO'S IN THAT PULPIT,
I CAN GUARANTEE THAT,

07:18.067 --> 07:22.299
AND MEMPHIS,
YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS IT.

07:24.300 --> 07:27.232
EXCUSE ME.

07:27.234 --> 07:29.632
IT'S GOING TO BE
A GLORIOUS EVENT.

07:29.634 --> 07:31.465
Man: YOU WANT TO FOLLOW US?

07:31.467 --> 07:35.065
♪♪

07:35.067 --> 07:36.932
-MAMA.
-JUST STAY CALM.

07:36.934 --> 07:38.598
MAMA, WHAT IS GOING ON?

07:38.600 --> 07:40.532
I HAVE FBI AGENTS ASKING ME
FOR MY LAPTOP.

07:40.534 --> 07:42.298
IT HAS SOMETHING TO DO
WITH YOUR FATHER, NO DOUBT.

07:42.300 --> 07:43.965
ALL OF MY ARRANGEMENTS
ARE ON THERE.

07:43.967 --> 07:45.032
THERE ARE NOT BACKUPS.

07:45.034 --> 07:46.565
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?
I KNOW I SHOULD'VE --

07:46.567 --> 07:49.398
CHARITY,
PLEASE, JUST FOR ONCE,

07:49.400 --> 07:52.065
CAN YOU FIND A WAY
TO BE USEFUL IN AN EMERGENCY

07:52.067 --> 07:53.999
AND NOT SOMEHOW MAKE YOURSELF

07:54.001 --> 07:57.798
THE NEEDY LITTLE CENTER
OF ATTENTION, JUST ONCE, PLEASE?

07:57.800 --> 08:03.865
♪♪

08:03.867 --> 08:07.665
OH, HEAVEN, HELP US ALL.

08:07.667 --> 08:09.465
WHAT ARE YOU -- OH.

08:09.467 --> 08:11.731
WHERE DO YOU THINK YOU'RE
GOING WITH MY COMPUTER?

08:11.733 --> 08:14.798
GRACE, GRACE, WHAT IS THIS?

08:14.800 --> 08:16.465
DOES THIS HAVE ANYTHING TO DO
WITH THE COURT CASE

08:16.467 --> 08:17.665
AND THAT CORALIE?

08:17.667 --> 08:18.865
THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THAT, MAMA.

08:18.867 --> 08:20.365
THIS IS ABOUT DADDY
AND THE IRS.

08:20.367 --> 08:21.832
THEY'RE TAKING ALL
OF OUR COMPUTERS.

08:21.834 --> 08:23.032
WELL, YOU'RE NOT TAKING MINE.

08:23.034 --> 08:24.332
LISTEN.
MY SERMON IS ON THERE,

08:24.334 --> 08:26.332
MY POWERPOINT,
MY MUSIC, EVERYTHING.

08:26.334 --> 08:28.665
-PLEASE, SIR.
-IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

08:28.667 --> 08:31.198
NO.
YOU, STOP RIGHT THERE, SON,

08:31.200 --> 08:33.732
OR I WILL RIP YOUR EARS
CLEAR OFF YOUR HEAD.

08:33.734 --> 08:35.398
I TOLD YOU SHE WOULDN'T
LET YOU DO IT,

08:35.400 --> 08:36.532
AND YOU CAN GIVE ME
BACK MINE NOW, TOO.

08:36.534 --> 08:37.999
MISS, STAND BACK, PLEASE.

08:38.001 --> 08:40.099
-LOG THIS INTO EVIDENCE.
-YES, SIR.

08:40.101 --> 08:41.631
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THIS IS ABOUT,

08:41.633 --> 08:43.932
BUT IF IT INVOLVES
JAMES GREENLEAF,

08:43.934 --> 08:45.632
IT DOES NOT INVOLVE ME.

08:45.634 --> 08:46.698
YOU MUST BE THE FIRST LADY.

08:46.700 --> 08:48.332
SHE'S THE PASTOR NOW.

08:48.334 --> 08:50.565
AND AN EX-WIFE,
FREE AND CLEAR.

08:50.567 --> 08:52.198
YOUR NAME IS ON
THE WARRANT AS WELL.

08:52.200 --> 08:55.132
Grace: THEY TRIED TO TAKE
MY COMPUTER.

08:55.134 --> 08:56.731
-GRACE.
-MAMA.

08:56.733 --> 08:58.531
-GRACE, WHERE IS YOUR FATHER?
-EXCUSE ME. EXCUSE ME.

08:58.533 --> 08:59.999
HE'S RIGHT THERE.

09:00.001 --> 09:01.199
THEY WON'T LET HIM BACK INTO
HIS OFFICE UNTIL THEY'RE DONE.

09:01.201 --> 09:03.332
ARE YOU -- PLEASE.

09:03.334 --> 09:05.132
HEY, MAMA, PLEASE.

09:05.134 --> 09:06.332
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

09:06.334 --> 09:08.999
GET OFF THE PHONE.

09:09.001 --> 09:10.865
GET OFF!

09:10.867 --> 09:13.065
I'LL CALL YOU RIGHT BACK, BUT
HAVE HIM CALL ME IMMEDIATELY.

09:13.067 --> 09:15.398
WHAT IS THE MATTER WITH YOU?
I AM TAKING CARE OF THIS, MAE.

09:15.400 --> 09:16.798
-I'M SOLVING IT.
-NO.

09:16.800 --> 09:17.998
I'M SOLVING IT.
YOU JUST BACK OFF.

09:18.000 --> 09:19.398
DIVORCING YOU WASN'T ENOUGH.

09:19.400 --> 09:20.732
I'M HANDLING IT.

09:20.734 --> 09:22.199
NOW, THERE'S BEEN SOME
KIND OF MISUNDERSTANDING.

09:22.201 --> 09:24.665
I HAVE DONE EVERYTHING I CAN TO
CUT TIES WITH YOU, EVERYTHING,

09:24.667 --> 09:27.265
BUT YOUR SIN
AND YOUR STUPIDITY,

09:27.267 --> 09:30.398
YOU DRAGGED ME RIGHT DOWN INTO
THE FIERY PITS OF HELL WITH YOU,

09:30.400 --> 09:31.732
AND I'M NOT GOING
TO LET IT HAPPEN.

09:31.734 --> 09:34.399
I'M NOT GONNA LET YOU DO IT.
I AM NOT.

09:34.401 --> 09:36.065
YOU HAVE NO RESPONSIBILITY
IN THIS AT ALL.

09:36.067 --> 09:37.298
THEY'RE TAKING EVERYTHING.
NONE.

09:37.300 --> 09:39.765
[ BEEPING ]

09:39.767 --> 09:42.698
[ PHONE RINGS ]

09:42.700 --> 09:45.032
PASTOR GREENLEAF,
GOOD MORNING.

09:45.034 --> 09:47.165
COUNSELOR GARNER, HOW SOON
CAN YOU GET DOWN TO CALVARY?

09:47.167 --> 09:49.865
AS SOON AS I NEED TO. WHY?

09:49.867 --> 09:52.065
-TAKE IT TO YOUR OFFICE, PLEASE.
-ALL RIGHT.

09:52.067 --> 09:55.299
WE NEED YOUR HELP.

09:58.134 --> 09:59.332
HERE'S WHAT THE FEDS
THINK HAPPENED,

09:59.334 --> 10:01.532
FROM WHAT I'VE BEEN
ABLE TO PIECE TOGETHER.

10:01.534 --> 10:04.865
JACOB TRANSFERRED $200,000
OF CHURCH FUNDS

10:04.867 --> 10:07.732
INTO WHAT TURNED OUT
TO BE A PERSONAL ACCOUNT.

10:07.734 --> 10:09.265
ALL RIGHT.

10:09.267 --> 10:12.065
FIRST OF ALL, I DIDN'T TRANSFER
ANY MONEY ANYWHERE.

10:12.067 --> 10:14.332
I DIDN'T DO THAT.
TASHA, SHE'S THE --

10:14.334 --> 10:16.765
SON, SON, LET THE MAN TALK.

10:16.767 --> 10:18.698
AND THEN YOU, BISHOP GREENLEAF,

10:18.700 --> 10:21.898
SO THEY THINK,
WITHDREW ALL THOSE FUNDS

10:21.900 --> 10:24.665
AND USED THAT AS A DOWN PAYMENT
TO THE IRS.

10:24.667 --> 10:26.099
I DID NO SUCH THING.

10:26.101 --> 10:28.099
ROCHELLE SET ME UP
WITH AN INVESTMENT ACCOUNT.

10:28.101 --> 10:30.332
LET THE MAN TALK, POP.

10:30.334 --> 10:32.599
DID YOU WITHDRAW $200,000
FROM THAT ACCOUNT, SIR?

10:32.601 --> 10:36.532
[ PAPERS RUSTLE ]

10:36.534 --> 10:40.132
YES. UM...

10:40.134 --> 10:43.465
YES, I DID,
BUT THIS IS MY ACCOUNT.

10:43.467 --> 10:46.398
THAT IS THE SAME ACCOUNT
THAT JACOB DEPOSITED

10:46.400 --> 10:47.798
TRIUMPH'S MONEY INTO.

10:47.800 --> 10:49.265
NO. NO. NO. NO.

10:49.267 --> 10:51.265
THIS IS AN INVESTMENT ACCOUNT,

10:51.267 --> 10:54.465
A CHURCH-BASED CRYPTOCURRENCY
INVESTMENT ACCOUNT.

10:54.467 --> 10:55.732
THERE IS NO SUCH ACCOUNT.

10:55.734 --> 10:56.865
AND HOW YOU COULD EVER
EVEN THINK

10:56.867 --> 10:58.532
THERE WOULD BE IS JUST STUPID.

10:58.534 --> 11:01.665
-WATCH IT!
-JACOB.

11:01.667 --> 11:04.231
MY MONEY MANAGER,
ROCHELLE CROSS,

11:04.233 --> 11:06.732
INSTALLED AN APP ON MY PHONE
THAT ALLOWS ME

11:06.734 --> 11:09.965
TO CHECK MY BALANCES
EVERY DAY AS IT COMES IN.

11:13.334 --> 11:15.998
I'M GETTING AN --
AN ERROR MESSAGE HERE.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.565
WATCH IT, POP.

11:17.567 --> 11:19.532
AND YOU OPENED A BANK ACCOUNT
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW ABOUT.

11:19.534 --> 11:21.165
-AND YOU SPENT MONEY THAT --
-HOW STUPID IS THAT?

11:21.167 --> 11:23.132
YOU SPENT MONEY THAT DOESN'T
EVEN BELONG TO YOU.

11:23.134 --> 11:26.098
BOTH OF YOU, JUST STOP IT.

11:26.100 --> 11:27.965
BOTH OF YOU GOT PLAYED
BY THESE WOMEN,

11:27.967 --> 11:31.965
AND BOTH OF YOU
PUT THIS FAMILY IN JEOPARDY.

11:31.967 --> 11:34.499
NOT TO MENTION THE FAITH
OF THOUSANDS OF INNOCENT PEOPLE

11:34.501 --> 11:38.365
IF WE DON'T DISPROVE THIS.

11:38.367 --> 11:40.632
WHAT CAN WE DO, MR. GARNER?

11:40.634 --> 11:42.998
FOR NOW, JUST WAIT.

11:43.000 --> 11:44.531
THEY OBVIOUSLY STAGED THIS RAID

11:44.533 --> 11:46.998
TO SEND A MESSAGE
TO OTHER CHURCHES,

11:47.000 --> 11:50.398
AND IF WHAT YOU ALL ARE SAYING
ABOUT THESE WOMEN IS TRUE,

11:50.400 --> 11:51.532
WE'LL FIGURE IT OUT.

11:51.534 --> 11:55.532
THERE'S ALWAYS A DIGITAL TRAIL.

11:55.534 --> 11:58.665
I'M FINALLY ON THE VERGE OF
TAKING CONTROL OF THIS CHURCH,

11:58.667 --> 12:01.598
AND BY THE TIME I DO --

12:01.600 --> 12:03.498
THERE WON'T BE ANY CHURCH LEFT.

12:03.500 --> 12:05.898
DO YOU KNOW HOW MANY DEMONS
WERE ON MY TAIL

12:05.900 --> 12:08.732
WHEN I LEAPT OVER
JORDAN INTO MY BLESSING?

12:08.734 --> 12:10.998
MAE, THIS IS HOW SATAN WORKS.

12:11.000 --> 12:13.832
RIGHT WHEN GOD'S ABOUT
TO BLESS YOU, HE BITES.

12:13.834 --> 12:17.765
WE CAN PUT TOGETHER A BRAND-NEW
POWERPOINT PRESENTATION.

12:17.767 --> 12:19.199
YOU CAN REWRITE THE SERMON,

12:19.201 --> 12:21.331
AND I BET IT'LL BE BETTER
THAN THE ONE YOU HAD.

12:21.333 --> 12:22.665
[ INTERCOM BEEPS ]

12:22.667 --> 12:26.932
WOMAN: Pastor Greenleaf,
Lionel Jeffries on line one.

12:26.934 --> 12:32.332
♪♪

12:32.334 --> 12:34.932
[ BUTTON CLICKS ]
-CALL BACK, PLEASE.

12:34.934 --> 12:38.431
♪♪

12:38.433 --> 12:40.299
HAVE YOU TALKED TO GRACE YET?

12:40.301 --> 12:49.498
♪♪

12:49.500 --> 12:51.631
AND MAKE SURE THOSE ARE UNPACKED
THE MINUTE WE GET BACK.

12:51.633 --> 12:53.099
AGENT DALLAS?

12:53.101 --> 12:54.765
MISS, YOU'LL GET YOUR COMPUTER
BACK AS SOON AS --

12:54.767 --> 12:56.965
IT'S NOT ABOUT MY COMPUTER.

12:56.967 --> 12:59.898
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

12:59.900 --> 13:01.365
SO WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

13:01.367 --> 13:06.398
YOU HAVE THE WHOLE REST OF
MY LIFE IN YOUR HANDS RIGHT NOW.

13:06.400 --> 13:09.132
WILL YOU JUST LET ME EXPLAIN,
PLEASE?

13:09.134 --> 13:13.098
THANK YOU.

13:13.100 --> 13:15.565
WHY ISN'T SHE TAKING
ANY OF YOUR CALLS?

13:15.567 --> 13:17.432
WHY IS THIS WEBSITE GONE?

13:17.434 --> 13:19.665
-HEY.
-HELLO, DARIUS.

13:19.667 --> 13:20.798
HELLO. COME ON.

13:20.800 --> 13:22.899
HEY, YOU HEARD WHAT HAPPENED?

13:22.901 --> 13:25.765
YEAH, FROM MY BOSS, ACTUALLY.

13:25.767 --> 13:28.665
YOU GOT A SECOND?

13:28.667 --> 13:30.332
GO, GO.

13:30.334 --> 13:32.398
YEAH.

13:32.400 --> 13:37.665
[ TELEPHONE RINGS IN DISTANCE ]

13:37.667 --> 13:38.832
HOW CAN YOU COME TO ME
LIKE THIS?

13:38.834 --> 13:40.265
I THOUGHT WE HAD A DEAL.

13:40.267 --> 13:41.865
OUR DEAL WAS THAT
I WOULDN'T COVER CALVARY

13:41.867 --> 13:44.999
AS LONG AS WE WERE TOGETHER,
AND I'M NOT COVERING THE STORY.

13:45.001 --> 13:46.631
NO, BUT YOU'RE A SOURCE,
RIGHT?

13:46.633 --> 13:48.031
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE ASKING ME
ALL THESE QUESTIONS

13:48.033 --> 13:49.232
'CAUSE YOU'RE A SOURCE.

13:49.234 --> 13:50.898
BECAUSE MY EDITOR
ASKED ME TO BE.

13:50.900 --> 13:52.898
AND THE ONLY REASON YOU'RE NOT
REALLY COVERING THIS STORY

13:52.900 --> 13:54.798
IS BECAUSE YOUR PAPER
WILL NOT LET YOU

13:54.800 --> 13:58.265
DUE TO A CONFLICT OF INTEREST
YOU WISH YOU DIDN'T HAVE.

13:58.267 --> 13:59.898
THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH OUR DEAL.

13:59.900 --> 14:03.665
ALL I'M ASKING YOU TO DO
IS CONFIRM A FEW FACTS,

14:03.667 --> 14:06.865
WHICH WILL COME OUT ANYWAY.

14:06.867 --> 14:10.598
THE FACTS ARE THAT
ROCHELLE JAMES AND TASHA SKANKS,

14:10.600 --> 14:14.465
PROBABLY WITH BASIE, HAVE
CONSPIRED TO WRECK MY FAMILY,

14:14.467 --> 14:15.965
MY FATHER.

14:15.967 --> 14:19.665
YOU KNOW ALL THIS.

14:19.667 --> 14:20.998
CAN YOU PROVE THAT?

14:21.000 --> 14:25.398
WHEN I CAN, I'LL LET YOU KNOW.

14:25.400 --> 14:29.898
JUST SAY WHAT YOU HAVE TO SAY.

14:29.900 --> 14:32.198
HAVE YOU EVER HEARD
THE EXPRESSION

14:32.200 --> 14:35.065
P.K., AGENT DALLAS,
PASTOR'S KID?

14:35.067 --> 14:36.465
I HAVE, AS A MATTER OF FACT.

14:36.467 --> 14:37.898
OKAY.
WELL, IT'S NOT A JOKE.

14:37.900 --> 14:42.465
IT'S A VERY REAL THING BECAUSE
WHEN YOU GROW UP IN THE CHURCH

14:42.467 --> 14:46.132
WITH SO MANY EYES ON YOU,
SO MUCH EXPECTED,

14:46.134 --> 14:48.398
IT FEELS LIKE
YOU'RE WALKING A TIGHTROPE.

14:48.400 --> 14:49.932
I CAN'T IMAGINE THE PRESSURE.

14:49.934 --> 14:54.465
WELL, THAT'S WHY A LOT OF P.K.s
DO SILLY THINGS SOMETIMES,

14:54.467 --> 14:56.132
JUST TO BREAK FREE.

14:56.134 --> 14:58.465
AND WHY ARE YOU
TELLING ME THIS?

14:58.467 --> 15:03.465
WELL, A FEW YEARS AGO,
I HAD SOME PICTURES TAKEN.

15:03.467 --> 15:05.465
I THOUGHT I WANTED TO BE
AN ACTRESS FOR A HOT SECOND,

15:05.467 --> 15:07.298
AND I LET A BOY
TAKE PICTURES.

15:07.300 --> 15:10.899
NOTHING TOO SERIOUS,
BUT MY MOTHER HANDLED IT,

15:10.901 --> 15:13.498
HAD TO PAY HIM,
AND THE WHOLE THING WENT AWAY.

15:13.500 --> 15:16.432
AND THOSE FILES
ARE ON YOUR COMPUTER?

15:16.434 --> 15:19.065
NO, THEY'RE ON HERS,

15:19.067 --> 15:20.332
SO IF YOU COULD PLEASE
JUST GIVE ME

15:20.334 --> 15:23.265
FIVE MINUTES WITH HER COMPUTER,
JUST FIVE MINUTES,

15:23.267 --> 15:25.598
I DON'T WANT ANYONE
TO SEE THOSE PHOTOS,

15:25.600 --> 15:27.832
ESPECIALLY SOMEBODY LIKE YOU,

15:27.834 --> 15:31.765
SOMEONE SO VIRTUOUS
AND UPRIGHT.

15:34.600 --> 15:38.465
I'LL HAVE TO SPEAK TO
MY SUPERVISORY SPECIAL AGENT.

15:38.467 --> 15:40.398
EXCUSE ME.

15:40.400 --> 15:43.732
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:49.867 --> 15:54.232
LOOKING FOR GRACE, PASTOR?

15:54.234 --> 15:55.898
YES, DO YOU KNOW WHERE SHE IS?

15:55.900 --> 15:57.898
NO, SHE LEFT A FEW MINUTES AGO

15:57.900 --> 16:00.732
BUT SAID SHE'D BE BACK
BEFORE GOING HOME.

16:00.734 --> 16:05.532
I CAN LET HER KNOW YOU CAME BY.

16:05.534 --> 16:09.065
THAT'D BE FINE. THANK YOU.

16:09.067 --> 16:12.332
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:12.334 --> 16:16.498
ALL I'M SAYING IS THE FBI
JUST ROLLED IN HERE,

16:16.500 --> 16:19.465
ASKING ALL KIND OF QUESTIONS,
RIGHT,

16:19.467 --> 16:20.665
AND I JUST FEEL LIKE
THE ONLY PERSON

16:20.667 --> 16:23.732
WHO CAN ANSWER
ALL THOSE QUESTIONS IS YOU.

16:23.734 --> 16:26.398
♪♪

16:26.400 --> 16:30.332
TASHA, HELLO?
DON'T HANG UP ON ME.

16:30.334 --> 16:32.132
I JUST DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

16:32.134 --> 16:34.398
I KNOW YOU OPENED THAT ACCOUNT.

16:34.400 --> 16:38.998
I KNOW YOU TOOK THE MONEY.

16:39.000 --> 16:40.465
BUT I ALSO KNOW THAT YOU
COULDN'T HAVE COME UP

16:40.467 --> 16:42.898
WITH THAT BY YOURSELF.

16:42.900 --> 16:46.832
BASIE PUT YOU UP TO THAT?

16:46.834 --> 16:48.098
BASIE IS GONE.

16:48.100 --> 16:52.665
WELL, ROCHELLE, MAYBE,
I DON'T KNOW.

16:52.667 --> 16:54.465
BUT WHATEVER AND WHOEVER IT IS,

16:54.467 --> 16:59.198
YOU HAVE GOT TO COME CLEAN
AND TELL THE TRUTH.

16:59.200 --> 17:02.265
LOOK, I PROMISE
I WON'T PRESS CHARGES,

17:02.267 --> 17:03.932
BUT YOU GOT TO HELP ME
OUT HERE.

17:03.934 --> 17:05.732
YOU GOT TO GET ME OUT
OF THIS JAM.

17:05.734 --> 17:13.932
♪♪

17:13.934 --> 17:16.198
♪♪

17:16.200 --> 17:18.598
-I'VE TOLD YOU WHAT I KNOW.
-TASHA.

17:18.600 --> 17:20.398
I DON'T KNOW NOTHING ABOUT
NO SECRET ACCOUNT

17:20.400 --> 17:22.332
OR NOTHING LIKE THAT.

17:22.334 --> 17:24.132
-I DON'T.
-OKAY.

17:24.134 --> 17:27.265
OKAY. OKAY, TASHA.

17:27.267 --> 17:29.699
♪♪

17:29.701 --> 17:33.632
[ Whispers ]
TELL HER YOU LOVE HER.

17:33.634 --> 17:35.632
TELL HER.

17:35.634 --> 17:42.798
♪♪

17:42.800 --> 17:46.598
TASHA, TASHA, I LOVE YOU.

17:46.600 --> 17:52.465
♪♪

17:52.467 --> 17:54.532
TOLD YOU.

17:54.534 --> 17:56.665
♪♪

17:56.667 --> 17:57.865
[ SCOFFS ]

17:57.867 --> 18:00.398
[ DIAL TONE ]

18:00.400 --> 18:03.665
[ BEEPS, TONE STOPS ]

18:03.667 --> 18:07.265
BASIE, I-I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S THINKING.

18:07.267 --> 18:09.732
YOU DON'T?

18:09.734 --> 18:11.665
BECAUSE I THINK I DO.

18:11.667 --> 18:17.665
♪♪

18:20.967 --> 18:23.498
HEY, CAMERON WANTED BARBECUE
FROM DVA.

18:23.500 --> 18:26.332
YOU GOOD WITH THAT?

18:26.334 --> 18:28.065
-I MEAN...
-I MEAN, I CAN GET SUSHI, TOO.

18:28.067 --> 18:30.065
YOU KNOW WHAT?
ACTUALLY, DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

18:30.067 --> 18:31.732
I GOT MAD DUDES
COMING TO THE STUDIO

18:31.734 --> 18:33.398
TO BANG OUT THIS RECORD.

18:33.400 --> 18:35.231
YOU CAN JUST HANG HERE,
ORDER IN.

18:35.233 --> 18:37.298
I ALWAYS COME TO THE STUDIO
WITH YOU.

18:37.300 --> 18:38.865
WHY?
YOU DON'T WANT ME TO COME?

18:38.867 --> 18:40.132
OF COURSE.

18:40.134 --> 18:41.665
IT'S JUST SOMETIMES YOU BE
SITTING OVER THERE

18:41.667 --> 18:43.732
LOOKING BORED OUT OF YOUR MIND.

18:43.734 --> 18:45.198
I FEEL BAD.

18:45.200 --> 18:48.665
I'M NEVER BORED OUT OF MY MIND.

18:48.667 --> 18:53.598
YOU KNOW WHAT? [ EXHALES ]

18:53.600 --> 18:56.932
HERE, TAKE THIS.

18:56.934 --> 18:58.665
GO GET YOUR NAILS DONE ON ME.

18:58.667 --> 19:00.865
ALL RIGHT? CHILL OUT.
I'LL SEE YOU WHEN I'M BACK.

19:00.867 --> 19:03.798
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

19:03.800 --> 19:08.065
OKAY.

19:08.067 --> 19:12.665
HEY, AND CAN YOU GET ME
THAT BOTTLE OUT THE CABINET NOW?

19:17.534 --> 19:20.465
[ BOTTLE CLINKS ]

19:20.467 --> 19:23.731
HERE. HAVE FUN. KILL IT.

19:23.733 --> 19:25.899
OKAY. SEE YOU LATER.

19:31.067 --> 19:33.299
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

19:36.000 --> 19:40.198
[ HORN HONKS IN DISTANCE ]

19:40.200 --> 19:42.065
GRACE, WHAT A SURPRISE.

19:42.067 --> 19:44.398
I DIDN'T EXPECT TO SEE YOU
IN MY OFFICE.

19:44.400 --> 19:46.265
DON'T TELL ME
CORALIE DOUBLED BACK INTO --

19:46.267 --> 19:47.432
CUT THE CRAP, ROCHELLE.

19:47.434 --> 19:49.465
I'M SORRY.
HAVE I DONE SOMETHING?

19:49.467 --> 19:52.599
I KNOW YOU'RE BASIE'S
HALF-SISTER.

19:52.601 --> 19:54.065
OKAY.

19:54.067 --> 19:56.498
-IS THAT A CRIME?
-NO.

19:56.500 --> 19:58.432
-BUT IT DOES GIVE YOU MOTIVE.
-MOTIVE TO DO WHAT?

19:58.434 --> 20:00.232
TO SET UP MY FATHER,
MAKE HIM PAY

20:00.234 --> 20:01.999
FOR THE DEATH OF YOUR FATHER.

20:02.001 --> 20:04.199
ARE YOU INSANE? YOU ARE.

20:04.201 --> 20:06.198
THAT CRYPTOCURRENCY INVESTMENT
WEBSITE YOU HAD

20:06.200 --> 20:08.065
MY FATHER GOING TO IS A DUMMY.

20:08.067 --> 20:09.465
IT NEVER EXISTED.

20:09.467 --> 20:10.865
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

20:10.867 --> 20:12.131
CRYPTOCURRENCY WHAT?

20:12.133 --> 20:13.732
THE FBI RAIDED CALVARY
THIS MORNING, ROCHELLE.

20:13.734 --> 20:15.865
PLEASE, STOP ACTING LIKE YOU
DON'T KNOW WHAT'S HAPPENING.

20:15.867 --> 20:19.065
AND STOP ACTING LIKE YOU DO.

20:19.067 --> 20:22.732
GRACE, I HAVE ENDURED
YOUR PARANOID PTSD BULLSHIT

20:22.734 --> 20:25.365
FOR MONTHS WITH PATIENCE,
OUT OF RESPECT FOR YOUR FATHER.

20:25.367 --> 20:28.232
NOW, I LITERALLY HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE AFTER HERE.

20:28.234 --> 20:29.832
YOUR FATHER HASN'T MENTIONED
ANY OF THIS TO ME,

20:29.834 --> 20:32.798
NOTHING, THE FBI, NOTHING.

20:32.800 --> 20:34.398
NOW, LAST NIGHT,
IN YOUR FATHER'S BED,

20:34.400 --> 20:37.432
I PROFESSED MY LOVE TO HIM,
AND HE DID THE SAME.

20:37.434 --> 20:38.765
THAT'S A LIE.

20:38.767 --> 20:40.898
AND HE TALKED TO ME IN EARNEST
ABOUT THE FUTURE WITH ME

20:40.900 --> 20:42.732
AT HIS SIDE
AND THE CHURCH AND IN HIS --

20:42.734 --> 20:44.799
-EVERYTHING YOU SAY IS A LIE.
-YOU KNOW WHAT, GRACE?

20:44.801 --> 20:47.932
I KNOW I CAN NEVER BE
A MOTHER TO YOU,

20:47.934 --> 20:51.331
BUT SHOULD YOUR FATHER
AND I DECIDE TO MARRY,

20:51.333 --> 20:54.131
MAYBE I CAN BE YOUR SISTER
IF YOU LET ME,

20:54.133 --> 20:58.198
BUT YOU'VE GOT TO LET
GO OF THIS MANIA.

20:58.200 --> 21:00.465
IT'S NOT OF GOD.

21:00.467 --> 21:02.532
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

21:02.534 --> 21:05.465
♪♪

21:05.467 --> 21:09.398
YOU CAN'T POSSIBLY THINK
THAT REMAINING IN THE PULPIT

21:09.400 --> 21:12.598
AT THIS POINT
IS BEST FOR THE CHURCH, CAN YOU?

21:12.600 --> 21:17.332
I THINK THAT WITH MAE ABOUT
TO FAN HER FEATHERS AND FLY OFF,

21:17.334 --> 21:21.299
CONTINUITY IN THE PULPIT
WOULD BE A-A SIGN OF HOPE.

21:21.301 --> 21:23.365
OR A SIGN OF A DEEPLY TIN EAR.

21:23.367 --> 21:25.265
MAE'S NAME IS ON
THAT WARRANT, TOO, CONNIE.

21:25.267 --> 21:27.031
I'M NOT HERE LOBBYING FOR MAE.

21:27.033 --> 21:28.965
WHAT ARE YOU HERE FOR, CONNIE?
BECAUSE THIS...

21:28.967 --> 21:30.698
I'M GIVING YOU FAIR WARNING

21:30.700 --> 21:33.098
THAT I'VE CALLED AN EMERGENCY
MEETING OF THE DEACON BOARD

21:33.100 --> 21:34.765
TO DISCUSS YOUR REMOVAL.

21:34.767 --> 21:36.865
AND WHO WILL YOU GET
TO PREACH HERE?

21:36.867 --> 21:38.798
I'VE REACHED OUT TO PHIL DEMARS

21:38.800 --> 21:40.932
OF THE HARMONY
AND HOPE MINISTRIES.

21:40.934 --> 21:44.798
HE'LL BE HERE NEXT WEEK TO VISIT
AND TALK ABOUT SOME CANDIDATES.

21:44.800 --> 21:47.332
CALVARY
IS AN INDEPENDENT CHURCH,

21:47.334 --> 21:50.565
AND I WILL NEVER LET IT BECOME
A PART OF ANY DENOMINATION,

21:50.567 --> 21:51.965
FULL STOP.

21:51.967 --> 21:55.198
THE FAITH OF THIS CONGREGATION
HAS LANGUISHED LONG ENOUGH

21:55.200 --> 21:58.765
UNDER THE SHADOW
OF YOUR ECCENTRICITIES.

21:58.767 --> 22:02.132
WE NEED LIGHT,
ACCOUNTABILITY,

22:02.134 --> 22:05.398
A FRESH START.

22:05.400 --> 22:07.598
THANK YOU, CONNIE.

22:07.600 --> 22:12.265
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

22:12.267 --> 22:17.599
YOUR OPINION REALLY
DOESN'T MATTER.

22:17.601 --> 22:19.332
NO, I DON'T -- YOU CAN'T...

22:19.334 --> 22:28.831
♪♪

22:28.833 --> 22:29.831
♪♪

22:29.833 --> 22:32.698
I CAN GET YOU A GLASS
IF YOU WANT.

22:32.700 --> 22:41.798
♪♪

22:41.800 --> 22:43.865
HERE, HERE.

22:43.867 --> 22:48.398
♪♪

22:48.400 --> 22:49.965
I'LL TAKE IT.

22:49.967 --> 22:52.631
[ PLATE THUDS ]

22:52.633 --> 22:54.665
-DON'T DO THAT.
-DON'T DO WHAT?

22:54.667 --> 22:56.498
DON'T PLAY-ACT LIKE
YOU'RE THE GOOD LITTLE WIFE,

22:56.500 --> 22:59.231
AND NOW YOU KNOW I KNOW
IT AIN'T LIKE THAT.

22:59.233 --> 23:00.999
-DON'T.
-I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG.

23:01.001 --> 23:04.599
I WAS OUT THERE EVERY NIGHT
ON THE ROAD

23:04.601 --> 23:08.665
OR IN SOME FLOPHOUSE TRYING
NOT TO GET MY ASS KILLED,

23:08.667 --> 23:12.465
PRAYING TO GOD, BEGGING HIM
TO PUT YOU IN MY DREAMS

23:12.467 --> 23:15.265
JUST SO I COULD SEE YOUR FACE,
AND THE WHOLE TIME,

23:15.267 --> 23:18.132
YOU WERE LOVING ON
JACOB GREENLEAF.

23:18.134 --> 23:20.232
HOW MANY TIMES DO I HAVE
TO TELL YOU?

23:20.234 --> 23:23.165
NOTHING HAPPENED,
AND EVEN IF IT DID,

23:23.167 --> 23:26.965
WHICH IT DIDN'T, YOU HAD ME
THINKING YOU WERE DEAD.

23:26.967 --> 23:28.832
TASHA, I KEPT
MY EXISTENTIAL STATUS

23:28.834 --> 23:30.998
A SECRET TO PROTECT YOU,

23:31.000 --> 23:34.598
IN CASE SOMEONE CAME LOOKING
FOR ME, ASKING QUESTIONS.

23:34.600 --> 23:36.665
-WELL, YOU TOLD ROCHELLE.
-LOOK.

23:36.667 --> 23:38.065
I KNEW IT WASN'T GOING
TO BE EASY,

23:38.067 --> 23:39.798
BUT I FIGURED IT ONLY GOING
TO BE A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

23:39.800 --> 23:43.598
IT AIN'T LIKE TASHA GOING TO
FIND SOMEONE NEW THAT FAST,

23:43.600 --> 23:46.332
BUT IT TURNS OUT,
YOU FASTER THAN I THOUGHT.

23:46.334 --> 23:49.698
NO, I'M NOT. YOU HAVE TO --

23:49.700 --> 23:51.798
I SAID DON'T.

23:51.800 --> 23:54.998
♪♪

23:55.000 --> 23:57.365
I DON'T TRUST YOU ANYMORE.

23:57.367 --> 23:59.165
-WHAT?
-AND TO BE PERFECTLY HONEST,

23:59.167 --> 24:03.631
I DON'T KNOW IF I'M EVER
GOING TO TRUST YOU AGAIN.

24:03.633 --> 24:05.565
BASIE. YOU...

24:05.567 --> 24:08.032
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

24:08.034 --> 24:12.398
[ VIBRATES ]

24:12.400 --> 24:14.065
YEAH.

24:14.067 --> 24:15.998
WHAT'S UP, BRO?

24:16.000 --> 24:18.432
[ SHUDDERS ]

24:21.367 --> 24:23.432
♪♪

24:23.434 --> 24:25.465
DARLENE, YOU KNOW
WHERE THE BISHOP IS?

24:25.467 --> 24:27.199
KORYN SAID
HE'S DOWN IN STORAGE.

24:27.201 --> 24:29.798
-OKAY.
-YOUR MOTHER'S LOOKING FOR YOU.

24:29.800 --> 24:32.132
[ LAUGHS ]

24:32.134 --> 24:34.932
OF COURSE SHE IS.
THANKS, DARLENE.

24:34.934 --> 24:36.932
WE'LL GET THROUGH THIS,
WON'T WE?

24:36.934 --> 24:40.598
IF YOU SAY YES,
I'LL BELIEVE IT.

24:40.600 --> 24:43.065
I DON'T KNOW.

24:43.067 --> 24:45.265
IT DON'T MATTER WHAT
GRACE GREENLEAF

24:45.267 --> 24:47.398
KNOWS OR THINKS SHE KNOWS.

24:47.400 --> 24:52.132
IF YOU AND TASHA DID LIKE
I SAID, BRO, WE'RE HOME FREE.

24:52.134 --> 24:54.265
WE NAILED ALL THOSE GREENLEAFS,

24:54.267 --> 24:57.931
TAKE THEM DOWN
AND THEIR CHURCHES.

24:57.933 --> 25:00.398
I SIGNED IT.

25:00.400 --> 25:03.298
I DON'T REMEMBER WHEN,
BUT THAT IS MY SIGNATURE.

25:03.300 --> 25:07.332
DAMN.

25:07.334 --> 25:10.065
[ SIGHS ] WELL, IT'S A GOOD
THING I DIDN'T QUIT MY JOB

25:10.067 --> 25:11.599
BECAUSE WE ARE DONE HERE,
JACOB.

25:11.601 --> 25:13.998
WE'RE DONE,
AND WE BARELY GOT STARTED.

25:14.000 --> 25:17.798
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]
-WHO IS THAT?

25:17.800 --> 25:19.465
IT'S TASHA.

25:19.467 --> 25:22.498
[ RINGS ]

25:22.500 --> 25:23.698
HEY, TASH.

25:23.700 --> 25:25.332
I WANT TO GET OUT OF HERE
TONIGHT,

25:25.334 --> 25:27.132
BE ACROSS THE BORDER
BY TOMORROW...

25:27.134 --> 25:29.132
CAN YOU MEET ME TONIGHT?

25:29.134 --> 25:31.265
YEAH, OF COURSE, WHERE?

25:31.267 --> 25:33.265
I'LL TEXT YOU THE SPOT.

25:33.267 --> 25:35.665
JACOB, I'M SCARED.

25:35.667 --> 25:37.132
HEY, DON'T -- DON'T WORRY.

25:37.134 --> 25:40.032
ALL RIGHT?
IT'S GOING TO BE OKAY.

25:40.034 --> 25:42.532
I HOPE SO.

25:42.534 --> 25:44.499
Basie:
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

25:44.501 --> 25:46.765
[ BEEPS ]

25:46.767 --> 25:48.432
SHE WANTS TO MEET.

25:48.434 --> 25:54.998
♪♪

25:55.000 --> 25:58.999
WHAT'S THAT LOOK FOR?

25:59.001 --> 26:00.665
YOU CARE FOR HER.

26:00.667 --> 26:01.965
I DO NOT.

26:01.967 --> 26:03.465
YES, YOU DO.

26:03.467 --> 26:07.865
I CARE ABOUT SAVING THIS FAMILY
AND OUR CHURCH, POPS, TOO.

26:07.867 --> 26:10.131
AND YOU CARE FOR HER.
I CAN SEE IT.

26:10.133 --> 26:11.865
OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT?

26:11.867 --> 26:14.132
I'M NOT HAVING
THIS CONVERSATION.

26:14.134 --> 26:17.732
I'M NOT GONNA HAVE IT
'CAUSE IT MAKES NO SENSE.

26:17.734 --> 26:22.898
[ CABINET THUDS ]

26:22.900 --> 26:25.265
WE'LL HAVE TO ROUND UP
ALL THOSE OLD PHOTOGRAPHS

26:25.267 --> 26:27.265
AND SCAN THEM AGAIN AND...

26:27.267 --> 26:29.065
IS THERE TIME TO DO THAT?

26:29.067 --> 26:31.299
IT TOOK WEEKS TO GET
THOSE BIDDIES TO HAND

26:31.301 --> 26:32.765
OVER THOSE PHOTOS
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

26:32.767 --> 26:34.431
WE'LL GET WHAT WE CAN.

26:34.433 --> 26:36.698
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

26:36.700 --> 26:40.432
-I WILL GET IT.
[ RINGS ]

26:40.434 --> 26:42.398
HELLO. PASTOR GREENLEAF.

26:42.400 --> 26:44.665
MAE, IT'S AARON JEFFRIES.

26:44.667 --> 26:47.932
AARON, WOULD YOU PLEASE
TELL YOUR FATHER THAT I'LL --

26:47.934 --> 26:51.132
HE'S DEAD, MAE.

26:51.134 --> 26:53.598
HE JUST PASSED.

26:53.600 --> 26:57.398
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

26:57.400 --> 26:59.931
WELL, I --
I'M SO SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

26:59.933 --> 27:03.798
YEAH, THEY STARTED HIM
ON A NEW CHEMO MEDICATION.

27:03.800 --> 27:07.865
HE HAD A BAD REACTION, AND HIS
SYSTEM JUST COULDN'T HANDLE IT.

27:07.867 --> 27:10.398
JUST THOUGHT YOU'D WANT TO KNOW.

27:10.400 --> 27:12.332
WELL, AARON, YOUR FATHER
WAS A GOOD MAN,

27:12.334 --> 27:13.598
AND HE HAD A GOOD LIFE,

27:13.600 --> 27:15.998
AND YOU HAVE EVERY REASON
TO BE PROUD.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.065
THANK YOU FOR SAYING THAT,
MA'AM.

27:17.067 --> 27:19.299
YOU LOOKING FOR ME?

27:19.301 --> 27:23.432
SO -- SO WE --
WE'LL TALK SOON, I'M SURE.

27:23.434 --> 27:28.165
-OKAY. BYE.
-BYE, NOW.

27:28.167 --> 27:29.098
[ RECEIVER THUDS ]

27:29.100 --> 27:32.099
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?

27:32.101 --> 27:33.431
UM, YES.

27:33.433 --> 27:39.832
I-I JUST WANTED TO SAY
THAT I KNOW IT WAS PRESUMPTUOUS

27:39.834 --> 27:42.332
AND INFANTILE OF ME,
HOW I SNAPPED THIS MORNING.

27:42.334 --> 27:45.798
I WAS JUST IN SUCH A STATE.

27:45.800 --> 27:50.665
WELL, I THINK WE ALL WERE.

27:50.667 --> 27:54.299
WELL, THAT'S IT. I'M SORRY.

28:01.467 --> 28:03.265
OKAY.

28:03.267 --> 28:05.865
UH...

28:05.867 --> 28:07.332
APOLOGY ACCEPTED.

28:18.767 --> 28:20.965
KORYN, PLEASE,
NOW GIVE ME A MOMENT.

28:20.967 --> 28:24.598
OF COURSE.

28:24.600 --> 28:27.732
AND HOLD ALL MY CALLS, PLEASE.

28:27.734 --> 28:37.132
♪♪

28:37.134 --> 28:42.532
♪♪

28:42.534 --> 28:44.398
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

28:44.400 --> 28:48.665
♪♪

28:48.667 --> 28:51.465
BISHOP.

28:51.467 --> 28:53.665
HOW CAN I HELP?

28:53.667 --> 28:56.731
TELL ME THE TRUTH.

28:56.733 --> 28:59.798
ALWAYS.

28:59.800 --> 29:00.998
DID YOU SLEEP WITH ROCHELLE
LAST NIGHT

29:01.000 --> 29:03.331
AND TELL HER YOU LOVED HER?

29:03.333 --> 29:04.332
NO!

29:04.334 --> 29:06.299
BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT
SHE TOLD ME.

29:11.700 --> 29:12.798
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

29:12.800 --> 29:18.598
TO SETTLE THIS ONCE
AND FOR ALL.

29:18.600 --> 29:22.065
♪ CHANGE, OOH ♪

29:22.067 --> 29:23.332
♪ CHANGE ♪

29:23.334 --> 29:28.198
♪ CHANGE, OOH, OOH ♪

29:28.200 --> 29:30.465
♪ AH ♪

29:30.467 --> 29:33.465
♪ SO GLAD HE CHANGED ME ♪

29:33.467 --> 29:35.598
♪ CHANGED MY WALK ♪

29:35.600 --> 29:38.598
♪ OOH, OOH, CHANGED MY TALK ♪

29:38.600 --> 29:42.365
♪ AH, AH, OOH ♪

29:42.367 --> 29:46.031
OH, MAXINE, IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

29:46.033 --> 29:47.365
OOH, THANK YOU, HONEY.

29:47.367 --> 29:50.365
-SO WHAT DID SHE SAY?
-WHAT DID WHO SAY?

29:50.367 --> 29:53.032
GRACE.
WHAT DID SHE SAY?

29:53.034 --> 29:58.732
OH, MAXINE, I NO LONGER HAVE
TO TALK TO GRACE ABOUT IT.

29:58.734 --> 30:00.265
LIONEL DIED.

30:00.267 --> 30:02.132
WHEN DID HE DIE?

30:02.134 --> 30:04.198
-THIS AFTERNOON.
-OH, OKAY.

30:04.200 --> 30:06.998
UH, ANTOINE, SOUND IS PERFECT,
DARLING.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.332
ARE YOU OKAY?

30:08.334 --> 30:10.965
YES, YES.
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I AM.

30:10.967 --> 30:14.132
YOU STILL HAVE TO TELL GRACE.

30:14.134 --> 30:16.065
WHY?

30:16.067 --> 30:18.598
I TOLD YOU, I DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF THIS MAN IS HER FATHER.

30:18.600 --> 30:20.465
WHY WOULD I PUT OUR FAMILY
THROUGH THAT?

30:20.467 --> 30:24.032
BECAUSE YOU HAVE TO,
BECAUSE YOU'RE ABOUT TO ASCEND

30:24.034 --> 30:26.565
INTO THE ROLE
GOD MADE YOU TO PLAY,

30:26.567 --> 30:29.698
AND IF SATAN HAS ANY HOOKS
IN YOU TO PULL YOU BACK DOWN,

30:29.700 --> 30:32.465
HE'S GONNA USE THEM,
AND WHO DO YOU THINK

30:32.467 --> 30:35.532
YOU ARE TO TELL
ANYONE ELSE ABOUT THE TRUTH?

30:35.534 --> 30:37.198
LOOK AT YOURSELF.

30:37.200 --> 30:40.532
YOU CAN'T TELL YOUR OWN DAUGHTER
WHO HER DADDY MIGHT BE.

30:40.534 --> 30:42.732
-YOU CAN'T ADMIT WHO YOU ARE.
-CAN YOU JUST --

30:42.734 --> 30:44.332
IS THAT THE VOICE YOU WANT
TO HEAR

30:44.334 --> 30:46.532
EVERY SUNDAY MORNING
IN YOUR HEAD?

30:46.534 --> 30:49.198
THE SISSY STUFF YOU'RE PULLING,
THAT'S FOR MEN.

30:49.200 --> 30:51.732
WOMEN SPEAK.
THEY TELL THE TRUTH.

30:51.734 --> 30:54.198
THE FUTURE MIGHT BE FEMALE,

30:54.200 --> 30:58.598
BUT IT WILL ONLY BE FANTASTIC
IF WOMEN TELL THE TRUTH.

30:58.600 --> 31:01.865
OTHERWISE, IT'S JUST GONNA BE
MORE THEFT AND SECRETS

31:01.867 --> 31:03.332
LIKE EVERY TIME
THAT CAME BEFORE.

31:03.334 --> 31:05.398
Woman: MS. PATTERSON?

31:05.400 --> 31:10.032
TELL GLORIA I NEED A HOT ROCK
MASSAGE AND THAT COCOA NIP TEA.

31:10.034 --> 31:14.865
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

31:14.867 --> 31:20.732
♪♪

31:23.767 --> 31:33.299
♪♪

31:33.301 --> 31:38.365
Look at bae, so serious.
[ Laughs ]

31:38.367 --> 31:41.165
Hey, what you hiding for?

31:41.167 --> 31:45.065
No, watch out.
What you doing?

31:45.067 --> 31:46.798
What's going on?

31:46.800 --> 31:48.265
Nothing.

31:48.267 --> 31:49.465
-Ooh.
-[ Laughs ]

31:49.467 --> 31:53.132
Stop it, you stop it.

31:53.134 --> 31:56.198
I'm getting back to work,
okay?

31:56.200 --> 32:05.632
♪♪

32:05.634 --> 32:10.265
♪♪

32:10.267 --> 32:12.798
HE SAID HE HAD TO TALK TO
HIS SUPERVISORY SPECIAL AGENT,

32:12.800 --> 32:14.865
AND HE NEVER CAME BACK.

32:14.867 --> 32:16.899
CARLTON, I'M JUST --
I'M WORRIED.

32:16.901 --> 32:19.398
OH, SHOOT, HE'S HERE.

32:19.400 --> 32:21.665
[ RECEIVER THUDS ]
-HEY.

32:21.667 --> 32:22.732
I'M SORRY IF I WAS OUT OF LINE.

32:22.734 --> 32:24.332
YOU WEREN'T.

32:24.334 --> 32:26.398
IF THE FILES ARE NOT RELATED
TO THE CASE, TURNS OUT,

32:26.400 --> 32:28.065
THEY CAN BE REQUESTED.

32:28.067 --> 32:30.998
-SO I CAN HAVE THEM?
-YES, MA'AM.

32:31.000 --> 32:33.232
BUT I'M GONNA HAVE TO TAKE
A LOOK AT THESE FILES

32:33.234 --> 32:36.532
BEFORE THEY CAN BE RELEASED.

32:36.534 --> 32:37.998
SO YOU HAVE TO SEE
THE PICTURES?

32:38.000 --> 32:42.398
I DO.

32:42.400 --> 32:44.665
THERE AREN'T ANY PICTURES.

32:44.667 --> 32:48.532
I KNOW.

32:48.534 --> 32:50.532
NOW, WHY DON'T WE TAKE A LOOK

32:50.534 --> 32:54.865
AT THE FILES
YOU REALLY WANTED, P.K.?

33:02.301 --> 33:03.365
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

33:03.367 --> 33:05.031
Heya.

33:05.033 --> 33:06.632
I TOLD YOU WHERE I WAS GOING.

33:06.634 --> 33:09.465
IS SHE WHY I COULDN'T COME?

33:09.467 --> 33:12.332
THE TEAM WANTED TO DO A LITTLE
MEET-AND-GREET THING,

33:12.334 --> 33:15.398
AND I KNEW IT WOULD BE PACKED.
ALL RIGHT?

33:15.400 --> 33:16.998
YOU KNOW THE A/C
OVER THERE BUGGING.

33:17.000 --> 33:19.065
COME ON.

33:19.067 --> 33:21.998
ARE WE EVEN REALLY TOGETHER?

33:22.000 --> 33:23.332
[ UTENSILS CLATTER ]

33:23.334 --> 33:26.198
[ SIGHS HEAVILY ]

33:26.200 --> 33:29.799
BABE, OF COURSE WE ARE.

33:32.200 --> 33:33.932
IT DOESN'T FEEL LIKE IT.

33:33.934 --> 33:36.865
BABY, COME ON.

33:36.867 --> 33:39.265
YOU KNOW YOU MY ONE AND ONLY,
RIGHT?

33:39.267 --> 33:42.098
YOU KNOW YOU MY FIRST LADY.

33:42.100 --> 33:44.098
WHAT ABOUT HER?

33:44.100 --> 33:47.632
SHE'S...A BURN.

33:47.634 --> 33:51.465
YOU THE ONLY ONE THINKING
ABOUT THAT GIRL.

33:51.467 --> 33:53.931
PROMISE.

33:53.933 --> 33:56.665
♪♪

33:56.667 --> 34:01.165
COME HERE.

34:01.167 --> 34:03.298
GIVE ME A KISS.

34:03.300 --> 34:04.965
MM, YOU SMELL GOOD.

34:04.967 --> 34:07.132
[ LAUGHING ]

34:07.134 --> 34:13.998
♪♪

34:14.000 --> 34:16.132
THERE.

34:16.134 --> 34:17.665
WHAT'S THIS?

34:17.667 --> 34:19.932
YOUR POWERPOINT PRESENTATION

34:19.934 --> 34:22.931
AND YOUR PHOTOS.

34:22.933 --> 34:24.332
USEFUL ENOUGH FOR YOU?

34:41.967 --> 34:46.498
HEY, STRANGER.

34:46.500 --> 34:49.332
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

34:49.334 --> 34:52.431
MY FATHER PASSED AWAY
THIS AFTERNOON.

34:52.433 --> 34:57.165
AARON, I'M SO SORRY.
COME HERE.

34:57.167 --> 35:00.732
IS THERE ANYTHING I CAN DO?

35:00.734 --> 35:03.931
MAYBE SIT DOWN FOR A MINUTE.

35:03.933 --> 35:06.598
YEAH, SURE.

35:06.600 --> 35:08.565
WHATEVER YOU NEED.

35:14.034 --> 35:15.899
THIS MUST BE SO HARD.

35:20.100 --> 35:22.765
IT'S EVEN HARDER
THAN YOU THINK.

35:22.767 --> 35:31.932
♪♪

35:31.934 --> 35:41.398
♪♪

35:41.400 --> 35:45.998
♪♪

35:46.000 --> 35:47.798
[ TOUCHSCREEN CLACKING ]

35:47.800 --> 35:55.432
♪♪

35:55.434 --> 35:59.965
BROTHER GREENLEAF.

35:59.967 --> 36:01.998
YOU EXPECTING SOMEONE ELSE?

36:02.000 --> 36:06.065
♪♪

36:06.067 --> 36:08.198
-WHERE'S TASHA?
-WHERE'S KERISSA?

36:08.200 --> 36:13.332
HOW ABOUT WE WORRY ABOUT
OUR OWN WIVES FOR A MINUTE?

36:13.334 --> 36:15.732
-YOU'VE BEEN BUSY.
-HOW SO?

36:15.734 --> 36:18.498
SETTING UP ME AND MY POPS.

36:18.500 --> 36:22.698
WHAT HAPPENED WITH YOU
AND TASHA?

36:22.700 --> 36:23.999
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

36:24.001 --> 36:27.332
IT'S NOT A DIFFICULT QUESTION,
PASTOR. WHAT HAPPENED?

36:27.334 --> 36:30.932
WHAT TRANSPIRED BETWEEN YOU
AND MY WIFE IN MY ABSENCE?

36:30.934 --> 36:34.765
WHAT HAPPENED?

36:34.767 --> 36:36.598
SO IT MUST HAVE BEEN SOMETHING
'CAUSE, "NOTHING,"

36:36.600 --> 36:40.299
TAKES ABOUT A SECOND TO SAY,
AND YOU AIN'T SAID IT YET.

36:40.301 --> 36:44.765
ON THE PHONE, YOU SAID,
"I LOVE YOU."

36:44.767 --> 36:47.632
YOU MEANT THAT
AS A CHRISTIAN, RIGHT?

36:47.634 --> 36:50.398
-WHATEVER HAPPENED WAS MY FAULT.
-I PLACE NO BLAME.

36:50.400 --> 36:52.932
-WELL, JUST DON'T BLAME TASHA.
-I PLACE NO BLAME.

36:52.934 --> 36:55.865
SIN IS SIN, AND THE WORLD
IS STEEPED IN IT.

36:55.867 --> 36:58.732
ALL GOOD.

36:58.734 --> 37:02.798
BUT WHAT HAPPENED?

37:02.800 --> 37:04.332
IF I GO HOME
BELIEVING THE WORST,

37:04.334 --> 37:07.332
THEN THE WORST
IS WHAT'LL HAPPEN.

37:07.334 --> 37:09.131
IT WAS JUST ONE KISS,
BROTHER. THAT WAS IT.

37:09.133 --> 37:11.532
I'M NOT YOUR BROTHER, BROTHER.

37:11.534 --> 37:13.499
ONE KISS, ONE.

37:13.501 --> 37:17.432
♪♪

37:17.434 --> 37:21.198
WELL, THANK YOU

37:21.200 --> 37:24.732
FOR YOUR HONESTY.

37:24.734 --> 37:27.732
IT'S MORE THAN I COULD GET
FROM HER,

37:27.734 --> 37:33.465
BUT THEY ARE
THE WEAKER SEX, RIGHT?

37:33.467 --> 37:37.398
BASIE...

37:37.400 --> 37:42.532
IT WAS NOTHING.

37:42.534 --> 37:46.932
I CAN SEE
IT WAS NOTHING TO YOU,

37:46.934 --> 37:49.665
BUT ONE MAN'S NOTHING
IS ANOTHER MAN'S EVERYTHING.

37:49.667 --> 37:53.598
♪♪

37:53.600 --> 37:55.598
OH...

37:55.600 --> 37:59.332
DON'T WORRY ABOUT TEXTING
TASHA NO MORE.

37:59.334 --> 38:01.332
I GOT HER PHONE RIGHT HERE.

38:01.334 --> 38:08.031
♪♪

38:08.033 --> 38:10.099
I'M ACTUALLY GONNA BE OUT
OF THE COUNTRY FOR A SPELL,

38:10.101 --> 38:12.432
SO I WOULD SUGGEST
YOU SELL THOSE NOW.

38:12.434 --> 38:15.098
ROCHELLE.

38:15.100 --> 38:17.298
I'M GONNA HAVE
TO CALL YOU BACK.

38:17.300 --> 38:19.465
OKAY, BYE.

38:19.467 --> 38:21.865
JAMES.

38:21.867 --> 38:23.732
I'M SORRY I HAVEN'T GOTTEN
BACK TO YOU TODAY.

38:23.734 --> 38:26.532
IF YOU CAN IMAGINE, I GOT A LATE
START THIS MORNING AND --

38:26.534 --> 38:29.532
YOU TOLD GRACE
WE SLEPT TOGETHER?

38:29.534 --> 38:30.798
I DIDN'T VOLUNTEER IT.

38:30.800 --> 38:32.465
IT CAME UP WHEN
I WAS DEFENDING MYSELF.

38:32.467 --> 38:35.365
-BUT THAT DIDN'T HAPPEN.
-IT DIDN'T?

38:35.367 --> 38:38.065
NO, AND YOU KNOW
IT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

38:38.067 --> 38:40.232
WHY WOULD YOU SAY SUCH A THING?

38:40.234 --> 38:41.232
JAMES, YOU REALLY
DON'T REMEMBER?

38:41.234 --> 38:42.432
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

38:42.434 --> 38:45.265
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT,
BABY?

38:45.267 --> 38:46.931
IS THIS SOME KIND OF
"MAN OF GOD,

38:46.933 --> 38:48.532
I DON'T DO THAT SORT OF THING"
TYPE OF AMNESIA?

38:48.534 --> 38:50.198
'CAUSE I CAN PLAY ALONG.

38:50.200 --> 38:52.065
ARE YOU DARRELL JAMES'
DAUGHTER?

38:52.067 --> 38:53.431
I AM.

38:53.433 --> 38:57.065
SO I ASSUME YOU ENTERED MY WORLD
FROM DAY ONE, CAME ONTO ME,

38:57.067 --> 38:58.998
GOT ME TO INVEST ALL THIS MONEY

38:59.000 --> 39:01.232
ALL WITH AN EYE
TO GET BACK AT ME.

39:01.234 --> 39:02.598
INVEST WHAT MONEY?

39:02.600 --> 39:05.798
-ROCHELLE.
-OH, YOU MUST STILL BE DRUNK.

39:05.800 --> 39:06.998
I DIDN'T KILL YOUR FATHER.

39:07.000 --> 39:08.998
I KNOW.

39:09.000 --> 39:12.131
MY FATHER DIED IN A FIRE
IN A CHURCH THAT YOU OWNED,

39:12.133 --> 39:15.798
A CHURCH THAT
YOU COULDN'T PAY UPKEEP ON.

39:15.800 --> 39:19.065
DO YOU THINK YOU KILLED
MY FATHER?

39:19.067 --> 39:21.831
IF I THOUGHT THAT, HOW COULD
I EVER BE IN LOVE WITH YOU

39:21.833 --> 39:23.431
OR DO WHAT WE DID LAST NIGHT?

39:23.433 --> 39:25.632
IT WOULDN'T MAKE SENSE,

39:25.634 --> 39:27.598
AND ABOUT THE INVESTMENT,

39:27.600 --> 39:29.665
WHATEVER YOU MEANT BY THAT,

39:29.667 --> 39:34.731
I DON'T MIX BUSINESS
WITH PLEASURE, SO LOOK.

39:34.733 --> 39:36.732
I JUST WANT EVERYTHING
TO BE OKAY AS IT --

39:36.734 --> 39:38.698
YOU GOT ME.

39:38.700 --> 39:43.665
YOU GOT ME.

39:43.667 --> 39:45.965
BUT YOU WON'T GET AWAY WITH IT.

39:45.967 --> 39:52.298
♪♪

39:52.300 --> 39:54.465
BITCH, I ALREADY DID.

39:54.467 --> 40:02.732
♪♪

40:02.734 --> 40:06.798
ANTOINE, CAN WE HAVE LESS TIME
IN BETWEEN EACH SLIDE?

40:06.800 --> 40:09.198
-SURE.
-AND THEN I THINK WE'LL BE GOOD.

40:09.200 --> 40:11.932
NO PROBLEM.

40:11.934 --> 40:15.899
OH. OH, GOD.

40:15.901 --> 40:18.298
GIRL.

40:18.300 --> 40:21.632
OH, YOU ALMOST GAVE ME
A HEART ATTACK.

40:21.634 --> 40:23.965
[ EXHALES ]

40:23.967 --> 40:25.532
LOOKS GOOD, MAMA.

40:25.534 --> 40:27.398
THANK YOU.

40:27.400 --> 40:28.998
YOU KNOW, YOUR SISTER
MOVED MOUNTAINS

40:29.000 --> 40:31.165
TO SAVE THEM FROM THE LAWMEN,

40:31.167 --> 40:35.565
AND HOW SHE DID THAT,
GOD ONLY KNOWS.

40:35.567 --> 40:39.365
ALL RIGHT.
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

40:43.134 --> 40:53.665
AARON JEFFRIES CAME TO SEE ME.

40:53.667 --> 40:57.531
SO YOU HEARD THAT, UH,
LIONEL PASSED?

40:57.533 --> 40:59.865
I DID.

40:59.867 --> 41:02.532
YOU KNOW, WE TORTURE OURSELVES
OVER THESE LITTLE DRAMAS,

41:02.534 --> 41:05.932
AND THEN DEATH SWEEPS THEM
ALL AWAY LIKE A TIDE.

41:05.934 --> 41:11.865
IT'S A SHAME
WE DON'T REMEMBER HOW, UM,

41:11.867 --> 41:17.665
SMALL THEY'LL SEEM IN THE END.

41:17.667 --> 41:19.332
WE'D BE MORE FORGIVING,
I THINK.

41:19.334 --> 41:26.265
♪♪

41:26.267 --> 41:28.132
IS LIONEL MY FATHER?

41:28.134 --> 41:36.798
♪♪

41:36.800 --> 41:39.665
I DON'T KNOW.

41:39.667 --> 41:49.932
♪♪

41:49.934 --> 41:54.865
[ SNIFFLES ]

41:54.867 --> 42:04.065
♪♪

42:04.067 --> 42:13.332
♪♪

42:13.334 --> 42:22.465
♪♪

42:22.467 --> 42:28.198
♪♪

42:28.200 --> 42:38.032
♪♪

